{"type": "article", "id": 23278, "title": "木梁存钱罐", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-04T07:30:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 59, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702133809H0SyLFfCI6s29Qeo.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">巴黎设计师 Sylvain Aebischer 利用开裂的旧木梁做了一组存钱罐。每一个存钱罐都是边长为 10 厘米的立方体，裂口成为投放硬币的口，很有隐蔽性。木材的天然纹路让这组存钱罐有了令人熟悉的手工感，是一个不错的废物利用的想法。每个存钱罐的纹路都不一样，可以购买，<a href=\"http://www.sylvainaebischer.ch/v2/spip.php?page=rubrique&amp;id_rubrique=6&amp;lang=en\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133807fzLWTXilZHjASsxy.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.60740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133808U2EjcJGPR1X6t5kF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.784375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133808Lxibolnmq1etO98E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}